	h2 Download

	h3
		a(class="download-link" href="./bin/crow.tar.xz").
			<crow-icon icon="download"></crow-icon> Linux x64

	| Run:
	<p><code>
		cd ~/Downloads
		<br />
		tar -xJf crow.tar.xz
		<br />
		cd crow
		<br />
		bin/crow run demo/hello
	</code></p>

	| This should print <code>Hello, world!</code>

	h4 Installing

	| Optionally, add this to your <code>~/.bashrc</code> (or equivalent):

	<p><code>export PATH="~/Downloads/crow/bin:$PATH"</code></p>

	| to make <code>crow</code> available on the command line anywhere.

